        "description": "Multi-pass (2-5) typical for layered contaminants on epoxy without single-pass overheating; 3 passes recommended for complete removal while preserving composite integrity. Single pass viable for light prep. Source: Industry case studies in Journal of Materials Processing Technology (2019); practical guidelines from laser cleaning service providers.",
